LHGB T686&lt;br&gt;
LT T68C, LB T68C&lt;br&gt;

- &lt;u&gt;Hyper Mini TOPLED®&lt;/u&gt;&lt;br&gt;
LB M676&lt;br&gt;

- &lt;u&gt;Mini TOPLED Santana®&lt;/u&gt;&lt;br&gt;
LG M470&lt;br&gt;
LS M47K, LO M47K, LY M47K&lt;br&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
Source: http://www.osram.convergy.de/</description>
